---
import Icon from "./Icon.astro";
---

<!-- <h2>My Strengths</h2> -->
<section class="box skills">
  <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
    <Icon
      icon="terminal-window"
      color="var(--accent-regular)"
      size="2.5rem"
      gradient
    />
    <h2>Technology and Software Driven</h2>
    <p>
      With a strong focus on leveraging cutting-edge technology and software, I
      strive to develop efficient and impactful solutions that drive business
      success.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
    <Icon
      icon="chart-line-up"
      color="var(--accent-regular)"
      size="2.5rem"
      gradient
    />
    <h2>Continuous and Adaptive Learner</h2>
    <p>
      As a continuous and adaptive learner, I thrive on expanding my knowledge
      and skills in technology while also exploring diverse subjects adjacent to
      or beyond the realm of tech.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
    <Icon
      icon="strategy"
      color="var(--accent-regular)"
      size="2.5rem"
      gradient
    />
    <h2>Collaborative Problem-Solver</h2>
    <p>
      I excel in collaborating with diverse teams while utilizing effective
      communication and problem-solving skills to tackle complex challenges and
      deliver results.
    </p>
  </div>
  <!-- Center view skills button div -->
  <div class="flex justify-center">
    <a href="/technical-skills" class="btn"
      >View Full List of Technical Skills</a
    >
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .box {
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .skills {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .skills h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
  }

  .skills p {
    color: var(--gray-400);
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--accent-regular);
    color: var(--white);
    border-radius: 0.375rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn:hover {
    background-color: var(--accent-dark);
  }

  @media (min-width: 50em) {
    .box {
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      padding: 2.5rem;
    }

    .skills {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 5rem;
    }

    .skills h2 {
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    }
  }
</style>
